Module frogger
Package frogger.model

Class Map

  • java.lang.Object
    • frogger.model.Map
  • public class Map
extends java.lang.Object

    Map

    The Map Class is used to contain all different types of Actor objects and provide the method for outside classes to access or add these objects.

    Use: 

                    Map map = new Map();
                map.getActor().add(.....);
    Since:
    1.0
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Wenzheng Shan
    See Also:
    Log, Obstacle, Turtle, WetTurtle, End, Digit, ImageView, Frog, Snake, Chomper, GameView, MapReader, MapFactory, GameController
